DP - Those who cant not remember the past are condemneed to repeat it ...


solving the DP - 

1 . Tabulation  - Bottom up DP

2 . Mamoization - Top Down DP  - Tend to store the vlaue of sub problems in some map / table .

How to know this is DP problems - 

1. Count the total number of ways .
2. Multiple ways to do this - but give min or max output .
3. When ever try all possible ways comes in .


###############  Shortcut ///////////////

1. Try to represent the problem in terms of index . 
2. Do all possible stuffs on that index according to the problem statement . 
3. Sum of all stuffs -> count all ways 
4. min( of all stuffs) -> find min